title: Female-Fronted Metal Videos (New Update 24)
description:
Yeah I know I said I was going to stop myself from uploading any more Vids....but it turns out i'm hopelessly addicted to these things so I hope you are too.
I translated the Russian titles to English as best as I could, on the few Russian vids that are in here,but I'm not a Linguist.
Lots of genres covered.
Lots of regions too.
Majority however are mostly in English
Quality is 480p to 1080p
Check out RockBitch and tell me if YOU wouldn't watch them perform live!
Please SEED and Enjoy and thanks to everyone that keeps me going....Bands and Fans alike!

PapaPitufo
